title: Animate add button if user has not pressed it
message:
Animate add button if user has not pressed it

We'll use a subtle animation on the add filter button to let the
user know they can interact with it (just in case it's not obvious)

title: Let the user know there is no XML with no filters
message:
Let the user know there is no XML with no filters

If there are no filters set up then it's not possible to show
the XML for the filters.  In this case we show a message to the user
indicating this is the case.
